{"tid":1399724,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"葵涌爆水管 路陷困九巴","createTime":"2019-08-03T09:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:18:12.000Z","uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"712b7e3ca034ce4727a2da069246e38f83b9825d","tid":1399724,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190803/photo/bkn-20190803094546399-0803_00822_001_03b.jpg?20190803162311\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190803%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190803094546399-0803_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20190803162311&h=8f374be2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190803/photo/bkn-20190803094546399-0803_00822_001_04b.jpg?20190803162311\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190803%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190803094546399-0803_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20190803162311&h=be2f7c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190803/photo/bkn-20190803094546399-0803_00822_001_07b.jpg?20190803162311\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190803%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190803094546399-0803_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20190803162311&h=e631d5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵涌禾塘咀街近葵興邨，今早(3日)8時24分，地底一條鹹水管突然爆裂，湧出大量黃泥水，並且出現路陷，面積約2.5乘1.5米；一輛來往荃灣西站至青衣長康邨43號路線九巴，剛巧駛至上址，左後轆陷入大洞中被困。由於路面出現水浸，乘客需要由警員協助下，經右邊太平門離開，事件中無人受傷。警方將路陷的一段路面封閉，以便水務署工人搶修。九巴安排拖車到場，並且在職員協助下，以木板放在路陷位置的上位，協助巴士駛走。<br />\n<br />\n九巴發言人表示，今晨一輛43線九巴駛經葵涌禾咀街近葵興邨，因路面凹凸不平及有水滲出，巴士左面後輪被困在路陷處。車長即時協助約20名乘客離開車廂，其後巴士拖回車廠再作詳細檢查。<br />\n<br />\n水務署發言人指，爆裂的鹹水管直徑150毫米，附近樓宇鹹水供應受影響，預計傍晚可恢復供水。"},{"pid":"4c4f250a25a433d785479d36d1c021c11e3e1497","tid":1399724,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1613579/org/27a3030c6a8765630340d79c4816d22c.jpg/mWvv0YkHQfN26yoO5d4eFeM-x7XowtZDewtSznsLUs4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1613579%2Forg%2F27a3030c6a8765630340d79c4816d22c.jpg%2FmWvv0YkHQfN26yoO5d4eFeM-x7XowtZDewtSznsLUs4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a68303a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82f6f50f8d766e00f876618750c775d0c0b2c62f","tid":1399724,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/meRF8Jp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmeRF8Jp.jpg&h=0f30ef1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019-08-02<br />\n九巴八月六日提供與新巴城巴所有聯營路線到站資訊<br />\n為協助乘客規劃行程，九巴將於八月六日 (下周二) 上午十時起，在手機應用程式App1933、九巴網頁及巴士站顯示屏，提供與新巴城巴所有聯營路線班次的到站時間預報資料。<br />\n<br />\n同時，新巴城巴之手機應用程式，亦可顯示所有與九巴聯營路線班次的到站預報時間。"},{"pid":"d70d1ab7d130453177dc236894a281e67fe696c7","tid":1399724,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好暴力"},{"pid":"ebae09b08765c9ceff46ca793a1200eb47740376","tid":1399724,"uid":168214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:19:02.000Z","msg":"如果下次遊行條喉自己爆點算"},{"pid":"4d260bfb7e383ba53e4ac0357e6ec3f70b1893b8","tid":1399724,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:20:10.000Z","msg":"渣電單車咪成個人跌能左落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ca338dd1bdefbba0c50b52c24f48d6721bc43a","tid":1399724,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:22:00.000Z","msg":"@nben"},{"pid":"9cf8fa9d48a55dd0de7e6d8c4816190a0894c6da","tid":1399724,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:24:01.000Z","msg":"嚴厲譴責咸水管爆裂 破壞路面 影響道路運作 堅定不移支持九巴行駛 對於有警察干預九巴內部運作予以強烈譴責及深表遺憾"},{"pid":"f8042737b892